name: Carol Condreay
description: I SEEK A GENUINELY SINCERE LOVING MAN BEYOND ANYONE I COULD POSSIBLY DREAM OF. I KNOW HE IS OUT THERE, & ANYTHING LESS THAN ME GIVING 100% IN ORDER TO FIND HER IS UNACCEPTABLE. ARE YOU WILLING TO TAKE THAT CHANCE, MAYBE 1 IN A MILLION, OR PERHAPS EVEN 1 IN A BILLION, TO FIND THAT PERSON YOU HAVE BEEN SEARCHING FOR YOUR WHOLE LIFE.
